<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 131</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General Business</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course plays a key role in the establishment of business management and operational structure after graduation. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation.
The content of the course basically consists of business functions, business management, human resources management in businesses, marketing and budget management.
In addition, it is aimed to gain leadership, teamwork, autonomy and guidance skills. The course will be conducted in a face-to-face education environment, therefore it will be carried out with teaching methods suitable for face-to-face education.
Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time. As a result, the preferred teaching method for the course and the skills to be gained are important at the post-graduation stage.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421822&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PSI 103</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical and practical scope of the course forms the basis of third and fourth year vocational courses and professional practices. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of the knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation. The course will be conducted in a distance education environment, therefore it will be carried out with teaching methods suitable for online education. In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, discussion-based learning activities will be included. These activities include answering discussion questions, in-class exercises, and group work.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421934&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ATA 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ataturk&apos;s Principles and History of Revolution II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Independence War, founding of the Turkish Grand National Assembly, international treaties, peace process, establishment of the Republic, Ataturk’s principles and revolutions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421886&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 118</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Medical Biology and Genetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.02.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Living systems, cell structure and function, the nature of the genetic material, DNA packaging and chromosome structure, RNA structure, synthesis and function, genetic code and protein synthesis the Human Genome Project, the basic principles of inheritance and mutation, recombinant DNA technology and the importance of the relationship between disease development and treatment with nutrition.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421860&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 126</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic Chemistry II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">With this course, the students of the Department of Nutrition and Dietetics are taught the theories and laws of important definitions, concepts, and laws related to Organic Chemistry; understanding reactions at the molecular level with organic chemistry; It is aimed to develop qualitative-quantitative thinking skills with laboratory applications.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421791&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 134</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Anatomy II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course is the basis of the vocational courses, professional practices and the branches of science supporting this field in the field of Nutrition and Dietetics in the third and fourth grades. The course contributes to the acquisition of evidence-based information, the use of research skills and the planning of scientific research, the integration of theoretical and applied knowledge of the field and outside the field. It contributes to the acquisition of the knowledge, skills and competencies required for the planning of the nutritional care process and its implementation within the framework of ethical principles. The course will be conducted remotely. It will be carried out with synchronous narration and online video applications, which are among the teaching methods suitable for distance education. Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time. In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, question-answer and discussion-based learning activities will be included. These activities aim to answer discussion questions, support in-class exercises and group work.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421792&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 136</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physiology II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.02.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course covers the physiological functioning of the respiratory, excretory, digestive, endocrine and reproductive systems. Topics such as gas exchange, liquid-electrolyte balance, acid-base regulation, which are the basis of the field of Nutrition and Dietetics, are discussed in detail, and the relationship of the systems with each other in terms of maintaining metabolic balance is emphasized. The functions of the gastrointestinal tract and the physiology of digestion are studied in depth to understand the absorption and availability of nutrients. In addition, the regulatory roles of hormones are discussed together with their effects on energy metabolism and reproductive health, and it is aimed that students understand the physiological basis of nutrition with a holistic approach</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421793&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BIL 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Computer II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical and practical content of the course is the basis of third and fourth grade professional courses and practices. It is aimed to gain the necessary knowledge and skills in Using Microsoft Excel, Introduction of Programs Used in Hospital, Creating Microsoft Access Database Objects Data Types, Microsoft Publisher Internet Environment, Internet Services, World Wide Web, Web browsers, Search Engines, File Sharing, Social Networks, Computer Security, and Project Development. Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time. For this purpose, teaching/teacher experiment by demonstrating in the lesson, demonstration/demonstration carried out by the teacher for teaching purposes, homework techniques will be used.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421794&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
