<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">24.02.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Prematurity, enteral and parenteral nutrition in infancy and childhood acute gastroenteritis, malnutrsiyon, are malabsorpsiyon, infectious diseases, childhood obesity, metabolic syndrome, eating behavior disorders, and medical nutrition therapy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421847&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
