<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition Education and Consuleing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical and practical scope of the course forms the basis of the fourth year applied vocational courses and professional practices, The course contributes significantly to the acquisition of the knowledge, skills and competencies required to plan and evaluate nutrition education for a specific group living in the community. Research shows that when students learn material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it longer. In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, 5. Presentation/Narrative, 8. Discussion based learning learning techniques will be included.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421910&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
