<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.02.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical and practical scope of the course forms the basis of vocational courses, professional practices and branches of science supporting this field in the field of Nutrition and Dietetics. The course contributes to the acquisition of evidence-based information, the use of research skills and the planning of scientific research, the integration of theoretical and applied knowledge of the field and outside the field. Planning of nutritional care process, autonomous/team work, professional advocacy and
It contributes to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for displaying attitudes and behaviors such as mentoring to colleagues and applying nutrition education and counseling within the framework of ethical principles. The course will be conducted according to the face-to-face teaching method. Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time. Your course is active
In order to facilitate the learning component, case-based learning, problem-based learning, discussion-based learning, personal/independent learning, homework, question-answer, brainstorming and observation learning activities will be included. These activities aim to answer discussion questions, support in-class exercises and group work.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421844&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
