<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course is in the nature of support for the fourth year graduation project courses in which the student will do research. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation. The course will be conducted face-to-face in a classroom environment. Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time. In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, problem-based learning and question-answer learning activities will be included.</Data></Cell>
