<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 401</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Seminar I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">02.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course, starting in the fourth grade and continuing after graduation, forms the basis of the ability to search current literature from the right sources and make effective presentations.
The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation.
The course will be conducted in a distance education environment, so it can be carried out with teaching methods suitable for online education and online video applications.
During the semester, it is important to gain the skills of researching and evaluating the latest scientific data related to nutrition and dietetics, discussing innovations and reporting and presenting the compiled information.
Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time.
In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, personal, independent learning technique will be included in the seminar article presentation activities. With this technique, it is expected that students will gain knowledge and experience in solving possible questions and questions about the prepared topic and in giving answers.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421893&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">BES 439</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Vocational Training in Clinical Nutrition-Children</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+18+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course contributes to the integration of theoretical and applied knowledge of the field and outside the field, and to gain the knowledge, skills and competencies required for the planning of the nutritional care process and its implementation within the framework of ethical principles.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421913&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
