<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course contributes to the integration of theoretical and applied knowledge, both field and non-field, and to gaining the knowledge, skills, and competencies required for the planning of the nutritional care process and its implementation within the framework of ethical principles.</Data></Cell>
