<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">02.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course is based on the student&apos;s theoretical knowledge and research skills acquired in undergraduate education. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of the knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation. The course will be conducted in a distance education environment, therefore, it will be carried out with teaching methods suitable for online education, question-answer and brainstorming practices. thus showing that they are stored for longer periods of time. Question-answer and brainstorming learning activities will be included to facilitate the active learning component of the course.</Data></Cell>
