<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course includes the concept of ethics and professional ethics, ethical rules in Nutrition and Dietetics education and practice, and case discussions.</Data></Cell>
