<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic genetic concepts, omics technologies, gene expression, nutrigenetics, nutrigenomics and epigenetics, inheritance patterns, genetic technologies, genetic variation, nutritional therapy in genetics and chronic diseases, genetic testing, ethical, legal and social applications, application of nutritional genomics in dietetics</Data></Cell>
