<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Carbohydrate counting method, the advantages and disadvantages of the carbohydrate count, carb count, the levels of the carbohydrate count for the proposed algorithm, the rate of insulin, carbohydrates, insulin sensitivity factor, insulin must be determined again when the rate of carbohydrates, glycemic index, glycemic load, carbohydrate content of foods</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421907&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
