<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By explaining the processes of DNA, RNA, and protein synthesis, you can explain the mechanisms of genetic information transfer within cells.</Data></Cell>
