<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">He/she is able to explain the physical, chemical and functional properties of carbohydrates, proteins, fats, enzymes, pigments, taste and odor components in the structure of foods.</Data></Cell>
