<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">He/she able to distinguish the properties, composition and principles of use of special nutritional products used in medical nutrition treatment of diseases in infancy and childhood.</Data></Cell>
