<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">He/she explain acute and chronic diseases seen in infancy and childhood and the importance of medical nutrition therapy in these diseases.</Data></Cell>
