<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Intro to European Movements: 1920’s
German Expressionism, Soviet Montage, and French
Impressionism
Films: Robert Wiene, German, The Cabinet of Dr. Caligari (1919)
Sergei Eisenstein, Soviet Union, [The Battleship] Potemkin (1925)
Luis Buñuel &amp; Salvador Dali, France, Un Chien Andalou (Andalusian Dog) (1927)
Impressionism</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=421857&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
