<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Science Fiction Horror (1980’s)
Reading: William Beard: “The Fly” In: The Artist as Monster. The Cinema of David Cronenberg.(Available on-line on Google Books.)Linda Badley:“The Darker Side of Genius.” Horror Film and Psychoanalysis. Cambridge UP: Cambridge, 2004. 222-240.
Film: Alien (R. Scott, 1979)</Data></Cell>
